<div style="background:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">
    <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/science/deaf-gene-therapy.html" style="color:#1a1a1a; text-decoration:none;">First Gene Therapy Restoring Hearing Gets FDA Approval</a>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; line-height:1.5;">
    "Otarmeni" restores hearing in children with otoferlin deafness. 80% of treated patients could hear without implants, and approximately 30% achieved fully normal hearing. This approval opens the door to treating over 150 genetic causes of hearing loss.
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#e8e8e8; color:#666; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px;">New York Times</span>
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#999; color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; margin-left:6px;">GENERAL INTEREST</span>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#4f9cf9; background:#eef5ff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:8px;">
    🔥 <strong>Critical:</strong> Landmark FDA approval — gene therapy is moving from experimental to real clinical use. Could transform treatment of genetic hearing loss.
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">
    <a href="https://www.reuters.com/science/nasa-rover-adds-list-organic-compounds-detected-mars-2026-04-21/" style="color:#1a1a1a; text-decoration:none;">Mars Organic Compounds — Strongest Hints of Habitability</a>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; line-height:1.5;">
    The Curiosity rover found 7 diverse organic compounds in a Martian lakebed rock, with 5 never before detected on Mars. While this doesn't confirm life, it demonstrates that Mars clearly had the right chemical ingredients for habitability.
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#e8e8e8; color:#666; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px;">Reuters</span>
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#999; color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; margin-left:6px;">GENERAL INTEREST</span>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#4f9cf9; background:#eef5ff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:8px;">
    💡 <strong>Key idea:</strong> Builds the scientific case that Mars sample return missions are worth the investment.
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">
    <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/science/reid-wiseman-earthset-photo-artemis-2.html" style="color:#1a1a1a; text-decoration:none;">First-Ever 'Earthset' Video Captured by Artemis II</a>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; line-height:1.5;">
    Astronaut Reid Wiseman recorded Earth disappearing behind the Moon's horizon during the Artemis II mission. The video went viral with over 11 million views, creating a modern sequel to Apollo 8's iconic Earthrise photograph from 1968.
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#e8e8e8; color:#666; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px;">New York Times</span>
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#999; color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; margin-left:6px;">GENERAL INTEREST</span>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#4f9cf9; background:#eef5ff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:8px;">
    ✅ <strong>Confirmed:</strong> Artemis program delivering on its promise — humanity is going back to the Moon, and this is the first visual proof in a generation.
  </div>
</div>

<div style="font-size:18px; font-weight:800; color:#1a1a1a; margin:24px 0 12px 0; padding-bottom:6px; border-bottom:2px solid #f08080;">
  🏥 HEALTH &amp; WELLNESS
</div>

<div style="background:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">
    <a href="https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2026/04/260425091216.htm" style="color:#1a1a1a; text-decoration:none;">Gut Bacteria Linked to Depression via Industrial Pollutant</a>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; line-height:1.5;">
    Harvard scientists identified a chain reaction: the bacterium Morganella morganii interacts with an industrial pollutant to produce a molecule that triggers inflammatory proteins linked to depression. This opens the door to immune-targeting treatments.
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#e8e8e8; color:#666; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px;">ScienceDaily</span>
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#f08080; color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; margin-left:6px;">HEALTH</span>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#4f9cf9; background:#eef5ff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:8px;">
    💡 <strong>Key idea:</strong> Could reshape depression treatment — targeting the gut instead of just the brain. Practical implication: gut health matters more than we thought.
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">
    <a href="https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2026/04/260422091043.htm" style="color:#1a1a1a; text-decoration:none;">Eye Injection Could Reverse Age-Related Vision Loss</a>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; line-height:1.5;">
    UC Irvine researchers found that injecting a specific polyunsaturated fatty acid directly into the eye restored visual function in older mice and reversed aging markers. The gene ELOVL2 controls production of fatty acids essential for healthy vision.
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#e8e8e8; color:#666; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px;">ScienceDaily</span>
    <span style="font-size:11px; background:#f08080; color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; margin-left:6px;">HEALTH</span>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#4f9cf9; background:#eef5ff; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:8px;">
    👉 <strong>Why this matters:</strong> Potential treatment for age-related macular degeneration, one of the leading causes of blindness. Relevant given your low-PUFA dietary lens.
  </div>
</div>

